ECHO PLAYER You feel a tingle as your atoms rearrange, then reform elsewhere.
  ECHO OTHERS %n slowly fades away.
  MOVE 2557
  AFFECT 2557
  ECHO OTHERS %n slowly fades into view beside you.
ENDIF  
